default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
default"Ninety-five per cent certain, is a pretty large degree of certainty - I recall that the number of people who think Elvis is still alive is round about five per cent," he [Tony Blair] added, to laughter.
